description:
For constantly changing trail conditions. When you're suiting up for a long day in the saddle, reach for this incredibly breathable jacket. The stretchy fabric is designed offer wind protection on long drops, and shed light precip when the weather turns grey. And if some blue sky appears, the whole thing packs into its back pocket.Recycled nylon face fabric with DWR sheds light rain and blocks wind.Circular knit backer is comfortable on your skin and improves moisture wicking.Stretchy fabric in an articulated design is comfortable for riding.Adjustable hood rolls down when not in use.2 zippered front pockets and 1 zippered interior pocket keep personal items secure.Rear drop pocket holds bulkier items.

